Vulture AI is a launcher/UI that ties together many excellent open-source
projects. It does not redistribute their code or model weights — it installs and
runs them on the user's machine. All credit for the underlying capabilities goes
to these projects and their authors. Please support them.

Bundled / orchestrated tools:
- ComfyUI                     — image generation backend
- ComfyUI-GGUF (city96)       — GGUF model loading
- Ultimate SD Upscale         — tiled upscaling
- ReActor                     — face swapping
- ComfyUI-LivePortraitKJ      — lip-sync / portrait animation
- ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite    — video I/O
- Ollama                      — local LLM runtime
- Open WebUI                  — chat dashboard
- Aider                       — local coding agent
- Qdrant + fastembed          — Code-RAG / semantic search
- TripoSR / Hunyuan3D         — image-to-3D

Models (downloaded by the user, each under its own license):
- FLUX (Black Forest Labs), Stable Diffusion 1.5 checkpoints,
  Qwen / DeepSeek / other LLMs, 4x-UltraSharp, inswapper + buffalo_l,
  LivePortrait weights, and others.

IMPORTANT: Several of these models/tools carry their own licenses, and some are
NON-COMMERCIAL. Review each project's license before any commercial use.
